                                        <due></due>
                            <votes>0</votes>
                                    <watches>2</watches>
                                                                                                                <comments>
                            <comment id="14624306" author="slebresne" created="Mon, 13 Jul 2015 07:17:13 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I guess we could just fix &lt;tt&gt;getDroppedColumnDefinition()&lt;/tt&gt;, but there isn&apos;t much point in using a &lt;tt&gt;ColumnIdentifier&lt;/tt&gt; in the map in the first place so I&apos;ve changed that. Simple patch attached.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14624533" author="iamaleksey" created="Mon, 13 Jul 2015 11:21:14 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;There is a typo in &lt;tt&gt;LegacySchemaMigratorTest:408&lt;/tt&gt; - &lt;tt&gt;UTF8Typ&lt;/tt&gt;, that makes tests not build.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Once fixed, there are issues with several tests that drop columns - &lt;tt&gt;CollectionsTest.testDropAndReaddCollection&lt;/tt&gt; is one of them.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Also, could you link to cassci after fixing these? Thanks.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14624751" author="slebresne" created="Mon, 13 Jul 2015 14:59:43 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Seems I had uploaded the wrong version, so attached the proper one (with unit tests &lt;a href=&quot;http://cassci.datastax.com/job/pcmanus-9781-testall/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;here&lt;/a&gt; and dtests &lt;a href=&quot;http://cassci.datastax.com/job/pcmanus-9781-dtest&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;here&lt;/a&gt;).&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14625154" author="iamaleksey" created="Mon, 13 Jul 2015 18:52:12 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;+1&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14626064" author="slebresne" created="Tue, 14 Jul 2015 09:02:20 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Committed, thanks&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
